[RELEASENOTES]

AnalogueTrash Records launched in late 2013 on the back of a
successful Manchester-based clubbing and live events brand. Set
up with the aim of bringing together and supporting artists to
release quality electronic music across the length and breadth of
the alternative and underground electronic music spectrum, 2014
has seen AnalogueTrash Records go from strength to strength.

To celebrate the first birthday of the label, AnalogueTrash
Records has released a free sampler containing 12 tracks
representing the diversity of the label's roster and really
showcasing the work of this talented bunch of artists and
producers. Do enjoy it, and please do check out the artists'
other releases.

[GROUPNOTES]
